name: SearchUsingStartingPoint
description: Service to discover EPA Office of Water linked program data.

inputParams.name: StreamSelectionType
inputParams.description: Navigation methodology for network discovery of linked data.
inputParams.label: Stream Selection Type

inputParams.name: StartingPoint
inputParams.description: Coordinate location to be indexed to the appropriate NHDPlus flowline from which to begin the navigation.
inputParams.label: Starting Point

inputParams.name: MaxDistanceKm
inputParams.description: Distance in kilometers to limit navigation. If MaxDistanceKm or MaxFlowTimeDay is not provided the full extent of the navigation will be returned. For certain configurations in large networks this is likely to timeout or otherwise fail to return results.
inputParams.label: Maximum Distance (Km)

inputParams.name: MaxFlowtimeDay
inputParams.description: Flow time in days to limit navigation. If MaxDistanceKm or MaxFlowTimeDay is not provided the full extent of the navigation will be returned. For certain configurations in large networks this is likely to timeout or otherwise fail to return results.
inputParams.label: Maximum Flow Time (Days)

inputParams.name: SearchForTheseLinkedData
inputParams.description: Choose linked data programs to discover during navigation.
defaultValue: Assessment, Total Maximum Daily Load Tracking and Implementation System (ATTAINS)
choiceList: Assessment, Total Maximum Daily Load Tracking and Implementation System (ATTAINS)
inputParams.label: Search For These Linked Data

inputParams.name: AttributeHandling
inputParams.description: Options for returning linked data program attributes.
inputParams.label: Attribute Handling

inputParams.name: ShowSelectedStreams
inputParams.description: Flag as to whether to return all flowlines of the navigation.
inputParams.label: Show Selected Streams

inputParams.name: AdvancedConfiguration
inputParams.description: Keywords reserved for advanced usage of the geoprocessing service.  Contact EPA Office of Water for more information.
inputParams.label: Advanced Configuration
